title: Germany 7 Year Note Yield
description: Germany 7 Year Bond Yield was 2.06 percent on Friday November 11, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the Germany 7 Year Note Yield reached an all time high of 4.77 in June of 2008. This page includes a chart with historical data for Germany 7Y.
author: Department of Treasury
